[[File:Werner_Stoetzer_Sitzender_Junge.jpg|thumb]]
'''坐'''是基本的人類休息[[姿勢|姿勢]]。體重主要由與地面或諸如[[椅|椅]]凳等水平物體接觸的[[臀部|臀部]]支撐，[[軀幹|軀幹]]則或多或少是直立的。生活中經常坐著會有顯著的健康風險，長時間坐著的人其死亡率比不常久坐的人要高<ref name="Biswas">{{cite journal |last1=Biswas |first1=A |last2=Oh |first2=PI |last3=Faulkner |first3=GE |last4=Bajaj |first4=RR |last5=Silver |first5=MA |last6=Mitchell |first6=MS |last7=Alter |first7=DA |title=Sedentary Time and Its Association With Risk for Disease Incidence, Mortality, and Hospitalization in Adults: A Systematic Review and Meta-analysis |journal=Annals of Internal Medicine |volume=162 |issue=2 |pages=123–32 |year=2015 |pmid=25599350 |doi=10.7326/M14-1651 }}</ref>。

有些[[跪|跪]]姿是是軀幹直立，將腿置於膝蓋以下，例如[[正坐|正坐]]及瑜珈中的{{link-en|金剛坐|Vajrasana (yoga)}}，有些情形下會將這種跪姿也歸類為坐。
==坐姿==
===席地而坐===
{{main|席地而坐}}
[[File:Frederick_Starr_wearing_Japanese_Kimono.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Renata_at_the_beach.jpg|thumb]]

跪坐在地上最常見的是屈膝而坐，一般可分為雙膝並排，或著是膝蓋彎曲盤腿而坐。也有雙腳伸直的坐姿，稱為踞坐。在[[東亞|東亞]][[漢字文化圈|漢字文化圈]]傳統中踞坐是極其隨便、無禮的坐姿。另一種是雙膝屈曲坐著，稱為“[[蹲|蹲]]坐”。

雙膝並排的有[[正坐|正坐]]，又稱[[跽坐|跽坐]]，是東亞傳統最正式的坐姿。而這種坐姿在[[瑜伽|瑜伽]]動作中稱為{{link-en|金剛坐|Vajrasana (yoga)}}。

[[盤腿坐|盤腿坐]]，一種稱為{{link-ja|胡坐|胡坐}}，是把雙膝彎起交疊而坐，用於冥想、修行的盤腿坐又稱[[跏趺坐|跏趺坐]]。
還有一種是一腿作蹲坐狀，另一腿盤起，稱為[[遊戲坐|遊戲坐]]。

箕踞，即两脚向前方或前方两侧伸展而坐，身体形状如箕。東亞古代妇女箕踞是被视为大不恭的。《[[韩诗外传|韩诗外传]]》记载：“[[孟子|孟子]]妻独坐箕踞，孟子入室视之，白其母曰：妇无礼。”<ref name="中国文化知识精华">《中国文化知识精华》，湖北人民出版社，ISBN：7-216-00281-4/G·18</ref>
{{clear}}

===坐在凳上===
[[File:DeTroy.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Börje_Ahlstedt_helfigur_sittande_(photo_by_Sune_Frack_on_Flickr).jpg|thumb]]
有[[凳子|凳子]]或[[椅子|椅子]]時，臀部、大腿坐在椅凳上，雙腳著地。

中国[[春秋时期|春秋]]时期，人們开始坐在六只足的矮床上，如果要写字、吃饭，就放上一张叫做“案”或“-{几}-”的矮小桌子。到了汉朝末期，北方[[胡人|胡人]]发明了一种可以折叠的“胡床”和一种新颖轻便的坐具“[[马扎子|马扎子]]”，即两木相交，中间穿绳，可张可合，人坐于其上，垂下双腿。这种坐具被胡人传入中原后广泛使用，被称为“胡座”，这种坐法也被称为“胡坐”。胡座也是中国椅子与凳子的前身，在胡坐的基础上，人们不断演变，在汉代后中国人逐渐有了坐于椅凳之上的习俗。<ref name="中国文化知识精华"/>

==健康風險==
十七世紀時{{le|貝納迪諾·拉馬茲尼|Bernardino Ramazzini}}所著的《論工人病》（De Morbis Artificum Diatriba），就將坐著列為「chair-workers」罹患疾病旳「奇怪姿勢」
之一<ref>{{Cite journal |pmc = 1446785|year = 2001|last1 = Ramazzini|first1 = B.|title = De Morbis Artificum Diatriba Diseases of Workers|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-public-health_2001-09_91_9/page/1380|journal = American Journal of Public Health|volume = 91|issue = 9|pages = 1380–1382|pmid = 11527762|doi = 10.2105/AJPH.91.9.1380}}</ref>。現今的研究發現長坐的人其死亡率會顯著的提高，若規律運動可以降低一些，但風險無法完全緩解<ref name="Biswas" /><ref name=":2" />。有關患病率及死亡率的原因有[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]、[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、[[2型糖尿病|2型糖尿病]]及[[癌症|癌症]]（特別是[[乳癌|乳癌]]、[[子宫内膜癌|子宫内膜癌]]、[[大腸癌|大腸癌]]、[[肺癌|肺癌]]及[[表面上皮间质肿瘤|表面上皮间质肿瘤]]）<ref name="Biswas" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title = Are workplace interventions to reduce sitting effective? A systematic review|journal = Preventive Medicine|date = Nov 2010|issn = 1096-0260|pmid = 20801153|pages = 352–356|volume = 51|issue = 5|doi = 10.1016/j.ypmed.2010.08.012|first1 = Josephine Y.|last1 = Chau|first2 = Hidde P. van|last2 = der Ploeg|first3 = Jannique G. Z.|last3 = van Uffelen|first4 = Jason|last4 = Wong|first5 = Ingrid|last5 = Riphagen|first6 = Genevieve N.|last6 = Healy|first7 = Nicholas D.|last7 = Gilson|first8 = David W.|last8 = Dunstan|first9 = Adrian E.|last9 = Bauman}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title = Sedentary behaviors and health outcomes among adults: a systematic review of prospective studies|url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-preventive-medicine_2011-02_40_2/page/174|journal = American Journal of Preventive Medicine|date = Feb 2011|issn = 1873-2607|pmid = 21238866|pages = 174–182|volume = 40|issue = 2|doi = 10.1016/j.amepre.2010.10.015|first1 = Karin I.|last1 = Proper|first2 = Amika S.|last2 = Singh|first3 = Willem|last3 = van Mechelen|first4 = Mai J. M.|last4 = Chinapaw}}</ref><ref name=":3" />。已找到坐著和心臟病、2型糖尿病死亡率之間的關係，但和造成癌症死亡率的風險還不清楚<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Wilmot|first1=E. G.|last2=Edwardson|first2=C. L.|last3=Achana|first3=F. A.|last4=Davies|first4=M. J.|last5=Gorely|first5=T.|last6=Gray|first6=L. J.|last7=Khunti|first7=K.|last8=Yates|first8=T.|last9=Biddle|first9=S. J. H.|title=Sedentary time in adults and the association with diabetes, cardiovascular disease and death: systematic review and meta-analysis|journal=Diabetologia|date=14 August 2012|volume=55|issue=11|pages=2895–2905|doi=10.1007/s00125-012-2677-z|pmid=22890825|url=https://espace.library.uq.edu.au/view/UQ:346455/biddle_affiliation.pdf}}</ref>。久坐時間也會和兒童及成年人[[重性抑鬱疾患|重性抑鬱疾患]]的風險有關<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Liu|first1=M|last2=Wu|first2=L|last3=Yao|first3=S|title=Dose-response association of screen time-based sedentary behaviour in children and adolescents and depression: a meta-analysis of observational studies.|journal=British Journal of Sports Medicine|volume=50|issue=20|pages=1252–1258|date=9 November 2015|doi=10.1136/bjsports-2015-095084|pmid=26552416|pmc=4977203}}</ref>。目前已找到久坐職業和較高[[身高體重指數|身高體重指數]]之間的相關性，不過還沒有找到因果關係<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title = Occupational sitting and health risks: a systematic review|journal = American Journal of Preventive Medicine|date = Oct 2010|issn = 1873-2607|pmid = 20837291|pages = 379–388|volume = 39|issue = 4|doi = 10.1016/j.amepre.2010.05.024|first1 = Jannique G. Z.|last1 = van Uffelen|first2 = Jason|last2 = Wong|first3 = Josephine Y.|last3 = Chau|first4 = Hidde P.|last4 = van der Ploeg|first5 = Ingrid|last5 = Riphagen|first6 = Nicholas D.|last6 = Gilson|first7 = Nicola W.|last7 = Burton|first8 = Genevieve N.|last8 = Healy|first9 = Alicia A.|last9 = Thorp|url = http://vuir.vu.edu.au/21403/|access-date = 2020-08-26|archive-date = 2019-01-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190128194512/http://vuir.vu.edu.au/21403/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。有關坐者是健康風險的原因，有很多的假說，例如因為肌肉長久沒有負荷造成的[[心輸出量|心輸出量]]、[[维生素D|维生素D]]、[[炎症|炎症]]、[[性类固醇|性类固醇]]活性、{{le|脂蛋白脂肪酶|lipoprotein lipase}}活性、以及{{le|GLUT4|GLUT4}}活性的變化等<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title = Sedentary behavior and cancer: a systematic review of the literature and proposed biological mechanisms|journal = Cancer Epidemiology, Biomarkers & Prevention|date = Nov 2010|issn = 1538-7755|pmid = 20833969|pages = 2691–2709|volume = 19|issue = 11|doi = 10.1158/1055-9965.EPI-10-0815|first = Brigid M.|last = Lynch<!--|doi-access = free-->}}</ref>。

